  "name": "Infectious Charms",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/spells/beam-magenta-3.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Wizard Arcane Discovery</strong><br/><br/><p>Your charms are so smooth that they're contagious. Anytime you target and successfully affect a single creature with a charm or compulsion spell and that creature is within 30 feet of another opponent, your spell has a chance of affecting the second creature as well. As a swift action immediately after affecting a creature with a charm or compulsion spell, you can cause the spell to carry over to the nearest creature within 30 feet. The spell behaves in all ways as though its new target were the original target of the spell. You must be at least an 11th-level wizard to select this discovery.</p>",
